Everything You Need to Know About Capcorp

Find answers to common queries about about Capcorp’s services, features, and how we make deliveries seamless and efficient!

What is Capcorp?

Capcorp is a centralized parcel delivery platform that connects users with courier companies and independent freelancers for fast, efficient, and affordable deliveries.

How does Capcorp work?

Capcorp allows users to select multiple pickup and drop-off locations. The platform sends the order to all drivers from connected courier companies and independent freelancers, ensuring the closest driver accepts the order.

Does Capcorp offer real-time tracking?

Yes, Capcorp provides real-time tracking, allowing you to monitor the status of your parcel from pickup to delivery.

Can I schedule deliveries in advance?

Absolutely! You can schedule pickups and drop-offs at your convenience to fit your personal or business needs.

What if no drivers are available nearby?

Capcorp’s marketplace integrates multiple courier companies and freelancers, ensuring broad coverage. If no drivers are immediately available, the platform notifies you with an estimated wait time.

Are independent freelancers reliable?

All freelancers on Capcorp are verified, and the platform tracks their performance to ensure reliable and professional service.
